@startuml seq_sec_bruteforce_defense
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title SOC · 暴力破解防御（滑动窗口）（论文风序号时序）

participant "客户端占位\nAuth Client" as CL
participant "边缘网关占位\nMiddleware" as M
participant "滑动令牌桶占位\nLimiter" as BK
participant "安全审计信道占位\nAuditSink" as S
participant "SOC速率计数占位\nSOC Panel" as K

CL -> M: 1. POST登录路径·附带网络指纹占位语义
activate M
M -> BK: 2. 递减窗口令牌配额占位
activate BK
BK --> M: 3. 放行语义或超限与重试延时占位摘要
deactivate BK

alt 窗口耗尽占位（拦截语义）

 M -> S: 4a. 写入爆破类超限事件占位

 activate S
 S --> M: 5a. ACK占位
 S --> K: 5b. 推送SOC速率卡刻度占位
 deactivate S

 M --> CL: 6a. HTTP429占位与Retry占位头

else 窗口仍有余量占位

 M --> CL: 4b. 附带配额响应头占位·继续应用链

end

deactivate M

@enduml


@startuml seq_sec_xss_edge_waf
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title SOC · XSS防护监测（论文风序号时序）

participant "访客占位\nBrowser" as CL
participant "边缘解码正则占位\nXSSEngine" as W
participant "403封堵页占位\nBlockPage" as P
participant "审计落点占位\nAuditSink" as LA
participant "SOC XSS占位\nSOC Panel" as X

CL -> W: 1. GET携带可疑QueryString占位矢量
activate W
W -> W: 2. 多重解码后与脚本钩子模式匹配占位

alt 矢量命中占位

 W -> LA: 3a. 写入XSS阻断类摘要事件占位

 activate LA
 LA --> W: ACK占位
 deactivate LA

 W -> P: 4a. 组装no-store防缓存占位HTML

 activate P
 P --> W: 页面体就绪占位
 deactivate P

 W --> CL: 5a. HTTP403可读拒绝占位
 W --> X: 5b. 推送SOC计数刷新占位语义

else 矢量未命中占位

 W --> CL: 6a. 放行至下级应用占位

end

deactivate W

@enduml


@startuml seq_sec_password_bcrypt_audit
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title SOC · 密码安全评估（慢哈希占位）（论文风序号时序）

participant "终端用户占位\nBrowser" as U
participant "登录路由占位\nLogin API" as F
participant "载荷形态预审占位\nInput Gate" as Z
participant "慢哈希核验占位\nHasher域" as H
participant "失败遥测账本占位\nAuthFailure" as AU
participant "SOC口令占位\nSOC Panel" as P

U -> F: 1. 发起登录·邮箱与口令仅内存占位
activate F
F -> Z: 2. 预审邮箱形态与口令长度阈占位

activate Z
Z --> F: 3. 结构合法占位或预审拒绝占位
deactivate Z

F -> H: 4. 提交凭证摘要比对占位
activate H
H --> F: 5. 核验通过或口令错误占位语义

alt 口令错误或凭证无效占位

 F -> AU: 6a. 写入掩码邮箱失败遥测占位

 activate AU
 AU --> F: ACK占位
 AU --> P: 6b. 推送口令安全卡刻度占位
 deactivate AU

 F --> U: 7a. HTTP401统一拒绝对外文案占位

 deactivate H
 deactivate F

else 核验成功占位

 F --> U: 8a. HTTP200与会话 Cookie 占位说明

 deactivate H
 deactivate F

end

@enduml


@startuml seq_sec_schema_validation_injection
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title SOC · Schema强校验与注入预防占位（论文风序号时序）

participant "API调用方占位\nCaller" as C
participant "统一入口门面占位\nGate" as H
participant "契约投影占位\nSchema" as Z
participant "拒绝审计账本占位\nValidationLog" as V
participant "业务处理核占位\nDomain" as DD
participant "SOC注入预防卡占位\nSOC Panel" as S

C -> H: 1. POST JSON占位·含商品订单键试探
activate H
H -> Z: 2. 白名单正则与类型投影占位演算

activate Z
Z --> H: 3. 契约通过占位体或违规项占位列表
deactivate Z

alt 违规项列表非空占位

 H -> V: 4a. 写入契约拒绝占位剪影

 activate V
 V --> H: ACK占位
